OL,3,CCharlotte Dujardin given six-month ban
OL,4,Cafter video shows 'error of judgement'
OL,6,FCharlotte Dujardin is out of the
OL,7,FOlympics and has received a six-month
OL,8,Fban over a video from four years ago
OL,9,Fshowing her making "an error of
OL,10,Fjudgement" during a coaching session.
OL,12,FThe International Federation for
OL,13,FEquestrian Sports (FEI) said it had
OL,14,Freceived a video "depicting Ms
OL,15,FDujardin engaging in conduct contrary
OL,16,Fto the principles of horse welfare".
OL,18,FThe video shows Dujardin repeatedly
OL,19,Fhitting a student's horse with a whip
OL,20,Ffrom the ground, according to the
OL,21,FDutch website horses.nl.
