OL,6,F"What happened was completely out of
OL,7,Fcharacter and does not reflect how I
OL,8,Ftrain my horses or coach my pupils,
OL,9,Fhowever, there is no excuse," she said
OL,10,Fin a statement.
OL,12,FDujardin added: "I am deeply ashamed
OL,13,Fand should have set a better example
OL,14,Fin that moment."
OL,16,FThe allegations are understood to have
OL,17,Fbeen raised with both the
OL,18,FInternational Equestrian Federation
OL,19,F(FEI) and the British Equestrian
OL,20,FFederation by a Dutch lawyer.
