OL,6,FThe three-time Olympic champion has
OL,7,Fwithdrawn from all competition whilst
OL,8,Fthe FEI continue to investigate.
OL,10,FIf she competed in Paris 2024, the 39-
OL,11,Fyear-old could have become Britain's
OL,12,Fmost decorated female Olympian.
OL,14,FA medal of any colour would have taken
OL,15,Fher clear of Laura Kenny, with whom
OL,16,Fshe is currently tied on six medals.
