OL,4,Cafter video shows 'error of judgement'
OL,6,FDujardin's statement continued: "I am
OL,7,Fsincerely sorry for my actions and
OL,8,Fdevastated that I have let everyone
OL,9,Fdown, including Team GB, fans and
OL,10,Fsponsors.
OL,12,F"I will cooperate fully with the FEI,
OL,13,FBritish Equestrian Federation and
OL,14,FBritish Dressage during their
OL,15,Finvestigations, and will not be
OL,16,Fcommenting further until the process
OL,17,Fis complete."
