OL,3,CCharlotte Dujardin given six-month ban
OL,4,Cafter video shows 'error of judgement'
OL,6,FDujardin was due to compete in both
OL,7,Fthe individual dressage and the team
OL,8,Fevent alongside Carl Hester and world
OL,9,Fchampion Lottie Fry.
OL,11,FShe is expected to be replaced in the
OL,12,Fteam by alternate Becky Moody and her
OL,13,Fhorse Jagerbomb.
OL,15,FDujardin is currently based in
OL,16,FGloucestershire. She and her previous
OL,17,Fpartner Valegro, known as 'the dancing
OL,18,Fhorse', trained in Newent and became
OL,19,Fhousehold names after winning double
OL,20,Fgold at London 2012.
